{"tid":163734,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"成功使用廢寵蝴蝶順利打爆寵物小精靈白金版","createTime":"2017-03-20T08:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T19:25:10.000Z","uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12e91b23477f6f4ad1f60a24acdedcf8f67dcdb5","tid":163734,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/17310918_1482687365076211_5584035186202005306_o.jpg?oh=49dcfae5aaf9dc69ae1c7efdc44508d0&amp;oe=5971CBA3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F17310918_1482687365076211_5584035186202005306_o.jpg%3Foh%3D49dcfae5aaf9dc69ae1c7efdc44508d0%26oe%3D5971CBA3&h=fe454b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n班連登仔成日唔鐘意人用勁寵打飛機,所以今次我就特登用垃圾狩獵鳳蝶同毒粉蝶去打柒四大天王飛機,進用殿堂紀錄,有圖實證,證明有愛有希望,就算唔用假面玫瑰電光獅勁寵都可以一take過!"},{"pid":"27d2bfc13e360f9c30dd86cefa8f749f65a8029f","tid":163734,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T08:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c8e9dadd9d0548a77d489b135723f801f6f257","tid":163734,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"大師兄同綠沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0628670109eb6cf7f5f83d40864d8c36938c2c0","tid":163734,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大師兄同綠沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有特別廢的寵自然有特別強的寵平衡翻啦"},{"pid":"387f4eb76e50bf05a13fe0c712818be1de35a57c","tid":163734,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T08:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444b65016c7c07704620c50f60f4f829c78afd3d","tid":163734,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply