ormal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時開台你咪知我點樣廢寵打飛機"},{"pid":"d96c8ef1712362667a7f0c35ccbc1b25e4724c7e","tid":163734,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係真就帶全垃圾啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n何謂全垃圾?全隊鯉魚王?"},{"pid":"03c5de0bc13898a840f416b37e280eb0f850a656","tid":163734,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係真就帶全垃圾啦</blockquote><br />\n真係全垃圾佢又過唔到呀麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a17d9f11ec4c12edf9de9be36d7ac23f151238","tid":163734,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係真就帶全垃圾啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n何謂全垃圾?全隊鯉魚王?</blockquote><br />\n係一隻鯉魚王"},{"pid":"b5f0eb22bbee7d968b186ff9dcacf53cef6242be","tid":163734,"uid":15427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:17:38.000Z","msg":"成功使用(其他寵carry)廢寵蝴蝶順利打爆小精靈白金版"},{"pid":"34c98462ec85f1036ac6e5b5c5d74bf9fb557858","tid":163734,"uid":34243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打飛機係應該自己打 唔使拎晒出黎show係街坊睇既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係冇人想睇(肯撚定)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004a018d67b00b0bbfab36af1220bc5c7dfb4460","tid":163734,"uid":32114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:28:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係真就帶全垃圾啦</blockquo